snippet.title: EpicTalez
snippet.description:
Stories! It's all about stories. I review fictional stories in books, anime, manga, movies and TV shows. I interprete some stories through animations and I get some of my friends to react to other stories. I am also a writer so I share writing tips. Check out my own story as well. It's called Cradle of chaos. 

I get my friends involved through reaction videos and writing tips ( My friend is a creative writing professor. Dont tell anyone.)
